{"tid":2266074,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"未擁有過一部ipod nano 3/4/5算唔算係人生遺憾？","createTime":"2020-11-01T04:06:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-24T02:36:32.000Z","uid":34884,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b69f98eb45d3e33c0b24441ccd5d91614777c9f1","tid":2266074,"uid":34884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T04:06:08.000Z","msg":"大概2006-2010左右<br />\n讀緊初中，未有Smartphone<br />\n好多手機連3.5mm耳機位都冇（尤其Sony Ericsson牙擦頭）<br />\n<br />\n嗰陣時既ipod nano真係好高汁<br />\n又彩moon又輕薄又多色<br />\n記得好多大陸同香港副廠最中意抄ipod樣(e.g. axk)<br />\n<br />\n細個又唔生性，為咗音質走去買咗部Cowon D2+<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大個睇返真係好後悔，因為ipod nano既設計真係有今生冇來世<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家已經冇乜人再買3000樓下既Mp3<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為電話已經做到晒聽歌影相功能<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d4QdN2v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd4QdN2v.jpg&h=aa5787da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tMwsSue.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtMwsSue.jpg&h=1bd230d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KTJSi9i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKTJSi9i.jpg&h=c9c02334&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xyTroA4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxyTroA4.jpg&h=c058f0b8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bbe4384f439c21255dfc22ea796cc2a8213be8f8","tid":2266074,"uid":113922,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T05:00:58.000Z","msg":"返學ipod shuffle 夾係袋<br />\n大把女女衝埋黎"},{"pid":"629b0e847f6646f99f8af22857d38a5d69629987","tid":2266074,"uid":109971,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T05:20:23.000Z","msg":"都唔明點解要停產<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dffa0b